{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_9", "eventName": "風暴瞭望", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "9-5", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "臨界值", "storyInfo": "號角向倫蒂尼姆發信無果。簡透過好友獲得了塔拉人聚會的情報，傳給了風笛。風笛和號角決定前去聚會一探究竟。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_offce", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$sjoyasorrow_intro", "key": "$sjoyasorrow_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "4:23 P.M. 天氣/多雲轉陰"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "麥克馬丁兄弟炸薯條專門店，二樓"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還是沒有回覆？", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_242"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有。從昨天到今天，沒有收到任何倫蒂尼姆來的消息。", "name": "廚子麥克馬丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "二十多個小時過去了，他們一定已經收到了我的上一封電訊。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "會不會是加密線路有問題？", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_242"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不好說啊長官。老實說，自畢業以後，我調來小丘郡都快十年了，需要啟動這條秘密通訊線路的情報就沒幾條。", "name": "廚子麥克馬丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_242"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "前年年末我跟我們小組長彙報，他問我除了第幾個孩子出生以外還有沒有話要說，沒有的話連常規報告都可以省了。", "name": "廚子麥克馬丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，怪不得你開了這家炸薯條店。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_242"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這主意不錯吧？誰讓我的代號一直是廚子呢。當時我就想，就算有外人想找我們的聯絡站，也只會懷疑隔壁書店。", "name": "廚子麥克馬丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔唔，而且炸薯條味道很好！", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_242"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是吧？哈哈，你們隨便吃。", "name": "廚子麥克馬丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小丘郡的馬鈴薯品質就是好。當地人很喜歡我的薯條，要不是還記著自己的點燈人老本行，我早就開了五六家分店。", "name": "廚子麥克馬丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_242"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎，總之，昨天你們用暗號找上門的時候，我還以為是又做夢夢到受訓時的事了。", "name": "廚子麥克馬丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#2"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......看起來這條線路是很可能被廢棄了。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#2"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#2"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "又或者，有人收到了消息，卻不想給回覆。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#2"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "隊長，你的意思是有人有意攔截我們的情報？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還不好說。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "下面這條訊息還是原樣發出去——對了，除了三角鐵的發現，再加上我和漢密爾頓上校的對話結果。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上校針對部分居民的措施已有過激嫌疑。萬不得已的情況下，我希望我們小隊能獲得更多機動權。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_242"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這......看來我沒必要勸你們動用駐軍信使了，是吧？", "name": "廚子麥克馬丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，隊長，我不想說這個，可我們人有點少。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這聽起來真不像你說出來的話。不過放心，沒人想走到那一步。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是......這座城市的情況，遠比我們來之前預料的更複雜。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "廚子，你在小丘郡待了這麼多年，你覺得這裡的人怎麼樣？", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_242"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒什麼特殊的。你真讓一個塔拉人站我跟前，我也不覺得他和其他地方來的維多利亞人有什麼區別。", "name": "廚子麥克馬丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_242"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再說句大實話，要是日子過得不錯，誰會整天想著鬧事？", "name": "廚子麥克馬丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_242"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "把理想掛在嘴邊的人挺多，真裝在心裡的走到哪都是少數。更多人在意的不過是填肚子，肚子滿了的話還有錢包。", "name": "廚子麥克馬丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說的是呀！隊長，我也很難把達米安·巴里和鬼魂部隊扯上關係。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在我眼裡，他和那條街上的居民都是普通人，被抓的時候會嚇得立刻求饒，親人死了會聚在一起崩潰哭泣。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們一點都不像受過訓練的士兵。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們說的，正是我所擔心的——漢密爾頓上校的話也許並不全是危言聳聽。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當普通人拿起了武器，無論他們是自願還是非自願，我們面臨的都將是一場維多利亞許久未見的災難。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "21_G3_victoria_street_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_213", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_213", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "下午好啊西爾莎！這麼巧，我剛想去報社找你。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#7$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_213", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "西爾莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_213"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_213", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咦，西爾莎，你怎麼了？你剛哭過嗎？", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_213", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......簡妮。不，我沒事，我很好。", "name": "西爾莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_213"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_213", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你騙人。你眼睛都腫了，而且臉色這麼蒼白，平時你可不會允許自己這麼狼狽地上街。你受到了驚嚇，對不對？", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_213", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是誰欺負你了？還是上次那個士兵嗎？我再幫你想想辦法......一定會有辦法的。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_213", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是的，簡妮，你別瞎猜了。他並沒有再來纏著我。", "name": "西爾莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_213"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_213", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是......我不知道怎麼說。", "name": "西爾莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_213"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_213", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來，深呼吸——在你面前的人是我，你的好朋友。你現在很安全，我保證。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_213", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——", "name": "西爾莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_213"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_213", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "簡妮......為什麼？為什麼你是他們中的一個？", "name": "西爾莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_213"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_213", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在說什麼啊西爾莎？我不明白。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_213", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不想你受到傷害。你是我最好的朋友......而且你是一個好人。我也是好人吧？我的媽媽、爸爸、表弟......我們不都是好人嗎？", "name": "西爾莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_213"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_213", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的表弟......巴里？你是說達米安·巴里？對不起，是我沒反應過來。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_213", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這不是你的錯。這也不該是我的錯。我只想要平靜的生活。我不想再看見重要的人死去了。", "name": "西爾莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_213"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_213", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......哭吧，西爾莎，我陪著你。看著親人離世，還要忙著工作，你壓力太大了。要不要靠在我的肩膀上？這樣能舒服一些。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#9$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_213", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用了，謝謝你，簡妮，看到你我已經好多了。現在我明白自己該怎麼做——", "name": "西爾莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_213"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_213", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個給你。", "name": "西爾莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_213"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_213", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是......一個地址？", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_213", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還可以給你幾個人名。但沒這個必要，我不想把你捲進更大的危險裡。", "name": "西爾莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_213"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_213", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個地址也該夠了。你可以......交給你覺得可靠的人。你的士官長，或者別的長官，比如路易士叔叔。", "name": "西爾莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_213"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道有人在打聽達米安的事，他們想弄清楚我們在謀劃什麼。", "name": "西爾莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_213"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_213", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謀劃——西爾莎，連你都......？！", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_213", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不清楚。信不信由你，從頭到尾，我只是負責傳遞一些消息。幾張夾在書裡的便條紙，一兩句藏在小丘晚報雜事欄裡的暗號。", "name": "西爾莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_213"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_213", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我以前以為這是為了讓大家更安全......我並不瞭解他們在盤算這麼可怕的事，直到我剛才聽見總編的通訊......", "name": "西爾莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_213"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算了，我不想辯解或者懺悔，更重要的是及時阻止他們。", "name": "西爾莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_213"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_213", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好，我會的。我想好了這東西該給誰。比起其他人，她能更公正地對待你們。西爾莎，你別怕，一切都會好起來的。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_213", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，簡妮，我相信你。", "name": "西爾莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_213"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_213", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "晚上八點，你要記得。拿好這個地址——", "name": "西爾莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_213"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "第十區雕像東側......左數第三個巷口。這裡有家書店，書店門口的花盆......黃色玫瑰......找到了。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "風......笛......收——", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（這樣壓在花盆底下就可以了嗎？剛好有塊鬆動的磚，和早上說的一模一樣。）", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#5$1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（這收信方式可真特別。）", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#5$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（倫蒂尼姆來的朋友，希望你能幫到西爾莎......和我們所有人。）", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_offce", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老闆，樓下有人新扔了一張紙條，在黃玫瑰下面。", "name": "麥克馬丁兄弟員工"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_242"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拿過來吧。", "name": "廚子麥克馬丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咦，黃玫瑰，給我的嗎？好快啊。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是你跟我提過的線人？", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。也是駐軍士兵，不過隊長放心，她是個熱心腸的好人。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#5"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......但願你慧眼識人。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#5"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒問題！我眼光一向很好。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#6"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "紙條上寫的什麼？", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#6"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“大壩街109號，今晚8點”——就這一句話。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_242"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大壩街？就在第十區和十一區交界處。這地方我有印象，是波頓男爵的房產。", "name": "廚子麥克馬丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來今天晚上會有一場重要的集會。風笛，我們該出發了。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "21_G9_rhodes_xqoffice", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_089", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_089", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......您在這裡。", "name": "幹員碎紙機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_089"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_089", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#6", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊。喝著熱茶，翻翻報紙，做我這個年紀的人該做的事。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#6"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_089", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖，風變大了。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_089", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "找到您想看的了嗎？", "name": "幹員碎紙機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_089"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_089", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#6", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（塔拉語）當你想找明天時，你卻與昨日相見。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#6"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_089", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#6", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您會說塔拉語？！", "name": "幹員碎紙機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_089"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_089", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#6", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "遠遠談不上會，如你所見，現學現賣而已。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#6"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_089", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#6", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......難以置信。奧利弗是對的，您非常厲害。", "name": "幹員碎紙機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_089"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_089", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，第一次讓人驚訝的時候我還會有些得意，第二第三次就難免無趣了。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_089", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們辦事處，大家基本都不會說塔拉語。", "name": "幹員碎紙機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_089"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_089", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "考慮到你們的出身，這很合理。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_089", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奧利弗成長於倫蒂尼姆北部的中產家庭，他們家族最早來自高盧，他至今住在辦事處樓上，每年都會請假回去看妻兒。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_089", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "弗雷德大約是來自半島郡的學徒，家中除了自己還有好幾個兄弟和一個小妹妹，家庭關係非常和睦。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_089", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "威爾是本地人，他們一家在幾十年前從附近的固定村落搬來小丘郡，他的塔拉血統應該是來自他的祖母。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_089", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......您看過我們的資料？", "name": "幹員碎紙機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_089"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_089", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#6", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我這麼怕麻煩的人，很少有提前做功課的習慣。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#6"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_089", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#6", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那您......怎麼知道？", "name": "幹員碎紙機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_089"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_089", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "語言。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_089", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "姓名、口音、措辭、語氣，甚至停頓的偏好——語言中含有的資訊比你想像的要多。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_089", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我對薩科塔的特殊之處有所耳聞，但沒想到......", "name": "幹員碎紙機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_089"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_089", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊哈，更多是我個人的小小興趣。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_089", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#6", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "話說回來，對於其他人而言，語言也有特殊的意義——否則，塔拉人也不會如此執著於從故紙堆裡把自己的語言找回來了吧？", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#6"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_089", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#6", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您說的對。在三五年前，並沒有多少塔拉人常說塔拉語。", "name": "幹員碎紙機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_089"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_089", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你呢？", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_089", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......您大概也聽出來了，我不是塔拉人。我的妻子是，她生前只教過我一兩句。", "name": "幹員碎紙機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_089"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_089", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可如今這種漸漸消失的語言在報紙上到處都是。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_089", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "另外，我剛才聽到窗外有人在教孩子們用塔拉語稱呼彼此。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_089", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......您提起之前，我沒發現。", "name": "幹員碎紙機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_089"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_089", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "語言的紐帶比許多別的東西都要牢固，不像血緣可能被流逝的時間沖淡，也不像利益時時刻刻都需要在天秤上經受衡量。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_089", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看樣子，有人想要利用這根紐帶，令一個本來日漸鬆散的群體重聚。可這麼一來，舊有的集合將不再穩固。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_089", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維多利亞不會放任這件事在眼皮子底下發生。然而拉扯的力量越大，反彈的力量就越超出預期。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_089", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們知道我因何而來，對吧？", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_089", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......其實，沒那麼清楚。我只覺得，取資料不用勞煩一名精英幹員親自跑一趟。", "name": "幹員碎紙機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_089"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_089", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "紙面資料不如親眼所見，這麼說的話，取資料也算不上幌子。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#2"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_089", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "麻煩再告訴我一遍，這半年來，有多少家當地企業與我們中止了合作？", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#2"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_089", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......七家。", "name": "幹員碎紙機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_089"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_089", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "比上個月報告的還多了三家。在今天的維多利亞，任何風吹草動，大商人們的錢袋子都會最先察覺。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_089", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也得出門再多看幾眼了——趕在泥雨將這座城市淹沒之前。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "21_G3_victoria_street_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "隊長，從上午到現在，你一直皺著眉。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我們剩下的時間不多了。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這一次鬼魂部隊的行動，和過去那些案件有所不同。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以前他們行事隱蔽，速度很快。每次我們想追上去的時候，都會發現線索全部被處理乾淨了。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而現在......", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，他們就像織完毛衣扔了一地線頭？線頭和線頭之間還沒什麼關聯。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#2", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......而且這些線索都斷在了小丘郡。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#2"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#2", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "隊長，不光是你，我也感覺悶得慌。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#2", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在這座城市，活像個出不了氣的高壓蒸鍋。居民，駐軍，大家都很煩躁，隨時隨地都有人在打架。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......大家都在等，等第一道雷什麼時候落下來。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但要是真落下來了，這座城市......不，維多利亞會變成什麼樣子？", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（隊長......！）", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#2", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（嗯？）", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#2"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#2", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#6", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（有人跟蹤！）", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#6"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#2", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#6", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（......確實。看到西邊那巷子了嗎？）", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#2"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#2", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#6", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（明白。）", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#6"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "21_G7_decisivebattlealley_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#6", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "站住！", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#6"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "jump", "power": 10.0, "times": 2.0, "fadetime": 0.51, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃啊——", "name": "克雷格"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咦，怎麼回事？是一個小孩子......而且還有些眼熟？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗚，痛......", "name": "克雷格"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，抱歉！我這就鬆手。我本以為跟進來的會是什麼壞傢伙。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......球。", "name": "克雷格"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是因為球掉了，所以想過來撿對不對？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "快點回家去吧，這地方不太安全，到處亂跑的話，你的爸爸媽媽會擔心的。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 358, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "隊長，虛驚一場。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8"}, {"id": 360, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#2", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......只是一個孩子？不，不太像。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#2"}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "跟著我們的人不止一個，而且能跟著走了幾條街，都沒有被我們發現，他們本身具備一定跟蹤經驗。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#2"}, {"id": 363, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你剛才躲在高處，還有沒有看到什麼不同尋常的人？", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 365, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊......一定要說的話，我瞥見不遠處的街道上有一個特別亮的圓環......", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 367, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......薩科塔。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 369, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "21_G3_victoria_street_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$farce_intro", "key": "$farce_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#6", "name2": "avg_npc_242", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#6", "name2": "avg_npc_242", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 請給我一塊蛋糕，還有這個蘋果派......那種餅乾也請給我來一些。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#6"}, {"id": 383, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_242", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......真是艱難的選擇，畢竟華法琳禁止我吃太多甜點......", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#2"}, {"id": 385, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#6", "name2": "avg_npc_242", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 你好，請問這些糕點中，哪種最甜？", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#6"}, {"id": 387, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#6", "name2": "avg_npc_242", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......", "name": "焦躁的青年"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 389, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#4", "name2": "avg_npc_242", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 難道你不知道？不會啊，你在小丘郡待了挺長時間了吧？我想，服役時間應該超過三年——", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#4"}, {"id": 391, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#4", "name2": "avg_npc_242", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......你？！", "name": "焦躁的青年"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 393, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#6", "name2": "avg_npc_242", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 別急啊，我能看出來，你跟著的人當然也能看出來。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#6"}, {"id": 395, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#6", "name2": "avg_npc_242", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 反正任務也沒法繼續了，不嘗嘗我買的蘋果派嗎？挺好吃的。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#6"}, {"id": 397, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#6", "name2": "avg_npc_242", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 你這奇奇怪怪的薩科塔，究竟從哪裡冒出來的？為什麼要阻攔我們的行動？", "name": "焦躁的青年"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 399, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#6", "name2": "avg_npc_242", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我？沒攔啊，我只是路過而已。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#6"}, {"id": 401, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#6", "name2": "avg_npc_242", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......", "name": "焦躁的青年"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 403, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#6", "name2": "avg_npc_242", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 十二隊，目標丟了，但看她們消失的方向，應該是去大壩街。", "name": "焦躁的青年"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 407, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#6", "name2": "avg_npc_242", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......好的，我明白，我馬上帶人去......", "name": "焦躁的青年"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 409, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#6", "name2": "avg_npc_242", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我們逐一排查。", "name": "焦躁的青年"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 411, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#6", "name2": "avg_npc_242", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我警告你，薩科塔，不該摻和的事情別摻和。", "name": "焦躁的青年"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 416, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#4", "name2": "avg_npc_242", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......警告？", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#4"}, {"id": 418, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#6", "name2": "avg_npc_242", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 類似的話聽得實在太多，沒什麼武器抵著我，還真不習慣。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#6"}, {"id": 420, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#6", "name2": "avg_npc_242", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......我現在沒空聽你耍嘴皮子。士兵們，我們走。", "name": "焦躁的青年"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 422, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "xpos": 300.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#6", "name2": "char_empty", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#6"}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 老闆，別害怕，士兵都走啦。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#6"}, {"id": 428, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#6"}}, {"id": 429, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 麻煩把剩下這些甜品都包一包，我帶回去給同事們嘗嘗。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#6"}, {"id": 430, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#2"}}, {"id": 431, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......畢竟，是時候把出門辦事的小朋友們都叫回來了。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#2"}, {"id": 432, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 433, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 435, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 437, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}